    • viewGymOwners

      List<FlipFitGymOwner> viewGymOwners()
      FlipFitAdmin Can View All the FlipFitGym Owners
      Returns:
      A list of FlipFitGymOwner objects representing all registered gym owners. If no gym owners are found, an empty list is returned.

    • viewGyms

    • viewUsers

    • verifyGym

      boolean verifyGym(int gymId)
      FlipFitAdmin Can Verify the Gyms and change their Status Like Verified Profile
      Parameters:

      Returns:
